## Conclusion
This project demonstrates:
- Handling user input in Java.
- Performing calculations and assigning grades.
- Using arrays or objects to store student data.
- Displaying results in a structured and easy-to-read format.

The menu-driven system allows easy addition and viewing of student records and can be extended for more features in the future.

